@startuml
title Azure OWASP Web Application Deployment and Performance Flow

actor Administrator
participant "PowerShell Script\nDeploy-AzureResourceGroup.ps1" as PS
participant "Azure Resource Manager" as ARM
participant "ARM Template\nLoadBalanced-Master.json" as Template
participant "Azure VNet" as VNet
participant "Azure Load Balancer" as LB
participant "Azure VM" as VM
participant "Azure Storage Account" as Storage
participant "ModSecurity WAF" as WAF
participant "ASP.NET MVC App\n(azure.owasp.web.adgroups)" as WebApp
participant "Azure AD" as AAD
participant "Node.js App\n(azure.owasp.waf.app)" as NodeApp
participant "Database\n(EF DbContext)" as DB

== Deployment Phase ==

Administrator -> PS: Execute deployment script
activate PS

PS -> ARM: Authenticate and connect
activate ARM

PS -> ARM: Submit ARM template deployment
ARM -> Template: Parse LoadBalanced-Master.json
activate Template

Template -> ARM: Orchestrate nested template calls
ARM -> VNet: Provision Virtual Network
activate VNet
VNet --> ARM: VNet created
deactivate VNet

ARM -> Storage: Create Storage Account
activate Storage
Storage --> ARM: Storage Account ready
deactivate Storage

ARM -> LB: Deploy Load Balancer
activate LB
LB --> ARM: Load Balancer configured
deactivate LB

ARM -> VM: Provision Virtual Machines
activate VM
VM --> ARM: VMs ready
deactivate VM

Template --> ARM: Template deployment complete
deactivate Template

ARM -> VM: Install ModSecurity
VM -> WAF: Configure ModSecurity with CRS 2.2.9
activate WAF
WAF -> WAF: Load base rules\nmodsecurity_crs_46_slr_et_*
WAF --> VM: ModSecurity configured
deactivate WAF

ARM -> VM: Deploy ASP.NET MVC application
VM -> WebApp: Install azure.owasp.web.adgroups
activate WebApp
WebApp -> WebApp: Configure Web.config\nOWIN Startup
WebApp --> VM: Application deployed
deactivate WebApp

ARM -> VM: Deploy Node.js application
VM -> NodeApp: Install azure.owasp.waf.app
activate NodeApp
NodeApp -> NodeApp: Configure Express routes
NodeApp --> VM: Application deployed
deactivate NodeApp

ARM --> PS: Deployment successful
deactivate ARM
PS --> Administrator: Deployment complete
deactivate PS

== Runtime Performance Flow ==

Administrator -> LB: HTTP Request to web application
activate LB

LB -> LB: Load balancing decision
LB -> WAF: Forward request
activate WAF

WAF -> WAF: Inspect request against\nModSecurity CRS rules
note right of WAF
  - XSS detection rules
  - SQLi detection rules
  - LFI/RFI rules
  - Joomla/WordPress rules
end note

alt Malicious Request Detected
    WAF --> LB: Block request (403)
    LB --> Administrator: Access denied
else Clean Request
    WAF -> WebApp: Forward validated request
    activate WebApp

    WebApp -> WebApp: OWIN middleware pipeline
    WebApp -> AAD: Authenticate user token
    activate AAD
    AAD -> AAD: Validate Azure AD credentials
    AAD --> WebApp: Token validation result
    deactivate AAD

    WebApp -> WebApp: Check Azure AD group membership\n(DatabaseIssuerNameRegistry)

    alt Authorized User
        WebApp -> DB: Query tenant/user data\n(EF DbContext)
        activate DB
        DB --> WebApp: Return data
        deactivate DB

        WebApp -> WebApp: Render MVC view\nwith jQuery, Bootstrap
        WebApp --> WAF: HTTP Response
        deactivate WebApp

        WAF -> WAF: Inspect response
        WAF --> LB: Forward response
        deactivate WAF

        LB --> Administrator: Successful response
    else Unauthorized User
        WebApp --> WAF: 401 Unauthorized
        deactivate WebApp
        WAF --> LB: Forward response
        deactivate WAF
        LB --> Administrator: Access denied
    end
end

deactivate LB

== Performance Optimization Flow ==

Administrator -> NodeApp: Request to Node.js app
activate NodeApp

NodeApp -> NodeApp: Express routing (minimal overhead)
NodeApp -> NodeApp: Render Jade template
NodeApp --> Administrator: Fast response (stateless)
deactivate NodeApp

note over WebApp, NodeApp
  Client-side performance:
  - jQuery for DOM manipulation
  - Bootstrap for responsive UI
  - Respond.js polyfill for IE
  - Modernizr feature detection
end note

@enduml
